{"title":"欢送邓副总理访美","authors":["赵朴初"],"dates":[{"year":1979,"month":1,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢送邓副总理访美"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——调寄西江月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赵朴初"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光景晴空万里，风云事业千秋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太平洋上看轻鸥，自在飞翔宇宙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"稳渡滔滔海浪，回旋小小寰球。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜听隔岸动歌喉，花雨缤纷满袖。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九七九年一月"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":3,"page_end":3}